## System 2 - Centralized Semi-Automatic Workflow

### Purpose

This system demonstrates a centralized semi-automatic AI workflow for the AI-Workflow-Nutrition project.
The workflow automates the full software lifecycle — from Design Thinking to code generation — using a single n8n pipeline powered by Ollama llama3 running locally.
At 3 key moments, the workflow pauses and waits for human validation before continuing.
This approach combines AI automation with human control to prevent error propagation and validate critical decisions.
<br>

