### Pipeline Steps
| Step | Description |
| --- | --- |
| 1 - Design Thinking | Generates user stories, personas and problem statement |
| 2 - Architecture | Generates global technical architecture |
| 3 - Production | Generates production specs with BLV API integration |
| 4 - Test & Improvement | Generates TDD test suites and quality gates |
| 5 - Security | Generates security analysis with vulnerability assessment |
| 6 - Deployment & Maintenance | Generates Docker and Azure DevOps CI/CD pipeline |
| 7 - Final Package | Consolidates all outputs into a full lifecycle report |
| 8 - Code Generation | Generates app.py Flask application connected to Swiss BLV API |
<br>
### Human Checkpoints
| Checkpoint | Trigger | Risk prevented |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Checkpoint 1 - Design Thinking | After step 1 | Wrong user story — wrong business understanding |
| Checkpoint 2 - Production | After step 3 | Invented BLV endpoint — hallucinated nutritional values |
| Checkpoint 3 - Go/No-Go Final | After step 6 | Unfixed vulnerability — incorrect deployment pipeline |
Each checkpoint has a 24-hour timeout. If not validated, the workflow stops automatically.
